## Instructions  
You are a professional communicator. Write an email to your team explaining that the Q3 roadmap is delayed by three weeks due to a vendor delay. Keep the tone professional but approachable, avoiding blame. Mention there is a mitigation plan in progress but details are not finalized. Clearly state what is changing and what remains the same.

## Input  
write an email to my team about our Q3 roadmap slipping by 3 weeks because of a vendor delay. keep it professional but not too corporate or stiff. dont blame the vendor or anyone on the team. mention we have a mitigation plan but i havent finalized the details yet. they need to know whats changing and what stays the same.